data.description: Welcome to luxury living in Oakleaf! This 4-bed, 3.5-bath home offers a well-designed layout and premium amenities. The formal living room welcomes you with natural light, while the adjacent family room is ideal for cozy gatherings. The gourmet kitchen boasts modern appliances and a convenient breakfast bar. Noteworthy features include Jacuzzi Pool, dual master bedrooms—one on each level—each generously sized with en-suite bathrooms and walk-in closets. The upper-level open loft adds versatility. Step outside to a private oasis with a covered lanai, paver patio, and heated in-ground swim spa. Parking is a breeze with the 2-car garage. A-rated schools and Oakleaf community amenities, including two clubhouses, pools, and gyms, enhance the lifestyle. Conveniently located, this home offers easy access to shopping and entertainment while maintaining suburban tranquility. Impeccably maintained, move in with confidence and start creating lasting memories. Schedule your showing today
